high_descs: Turn around and stand next to the tub, facing the toilet.
Pick the candle up from the side of the tub.
Move to the left a bit to face the toilet.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and stand next to the tub facing the sink.
Pick the candle up from the side of the tub.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the candle on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles on the back of a toilet.

high_descs: walk to face top end of bath tub
pick up candle stick from edge of tub
turn to face toilet
put candle stick on toilet tank lid
turn to face end of bath tub
pick up candle stick from edge of tub
turn to face toilet
put candle stick on toilet tank lid
anns.task_desc: put two candle sticks on toilet tank lid

high_descs: Turn around walk to the toilet and face it
pick up the candle that was on the tub
move in front of the toilet and face it
place the candle on top of the toilet lid in front of the left spray
turn around and face the sink that was behind you
pick up the other candle that was on the tub's edge
turn around and face the toilet
place the candle to the left of the other candle that is on the toilet
anns.task_desc: pick up both candles that are on the tub and move them to the top of the toilet by the left spray.
